    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>什么是The Enigma Case？🕵️‍♂️</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Enigma Cases</strong> 是一款支持 1–4 人合作的侦探游戏，背景设定在 2000 年代美国的虚构小镇桑德伍德。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >调查犯罪现场，收集并分析实体与数字证据，追踪嫌疑人，并在警局进行审讯，逐步揭开案件真相。你的每一个决定都会影响调查进展。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/d9b28c2b58591ceffe5221eff87e9ea1.poster.avif?t=1771279558\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/d9b28c2b58591ceffe5221eff87e9ea1.webm?t=1771279558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/d9b28c2b58591ceffe5221eff87e9ea1.mp4?t=1771279558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >各种案例</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个案件都有独立的故事，包括谋杀、事故和可疑死亡。每一次调查都不尽相同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索真实还原的地点，从咖啡馆、公寓到高速公路和限制区域，每个场景都隐藏着关键线索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/0b33d8a92df28bd2f8fac48e816a9d4a.poster.avif?t=1771279558\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/0b33d8a92df28bd2f8fac48e816a9d4a.webm?t=1771279558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/0b33d8a92df28bd2f8fac48e816a9d4a.mp4?t=1771279558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >侦探角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >调查过程基于不同的角色分工。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>现场侦探</strong>负责收集实体证据、勘查现场并直接审问嫌疑人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>网络侦探</strong>则分析电子邮件、GPS 记录、社交媒体、数据库和安防系统中的数字线索。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/f600dc1e75ade4f3279718b80487508d.poster.avif?t=1771279558\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/f600dc1e75ade4f3279718b80487508d.webm?t=1771279558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/f600dc1e75ade4f3279718b80487508d.mp4?t=1771279558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多人合作</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持 1–4 人合作破案。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位玩家承担不同职责，共享信息并整合证据。团队协作至关重要。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/6db2ab1ffe699d78cf5283d5af2be877.poster.avif?t=1771279558\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/6db2ab1ffe699d78cf5283d5af2be877.webm?t=1771279558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/6db2ab1ffe699d78cf5283d5af2be877.mp4?t=1771279558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>深度调查</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用警局内的专业工具推进案件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分析监控录像、DNA 痕迹、受限数据库，修复损坏的音频记录，并研究法医和毒理报告。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>真实且沉浸的故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个案件都围绕细致的人物、真实的环境和精心编写的剧情展开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >调查受害者的住所、机密文件、隐藏房间、保险箱和安防系统，体验心理紧张与意外结局。  <br>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>加入愿望单</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将 <strong>The Enigma Cases</strong> 添加至愿望单，并加入我们的 Discord。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.poster.avif?t=1771279558\" width=736 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.webm?t=1771279558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.mp4?t=1771279558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
